  "instructions": [
    "Heat the donabe to 210°C over medium heat.",
    "Add the ghee, grated ginger, and garlic to the donabe and cook for 3 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the boneless chicken thighs to the donabe and cook for 15 minutes, or until browned and cooked through.",
    "Add the fermented chili paste to the donabe and stir to combine.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix the soured cream and chopped chives.",
    "To assemble the wrap, place a portion of the chicken mixture onto a pita bread, followed by a dollop of the soured cream mixture, and finally a handful of mixed greens.",
    "Wrap the pita bread tightly and serve with a lemon wedge on the side."
